snippet.title: Dead by Daylight - Nicolas Cage Trailer | Summer Game Fest 2023
snippet.description:
Dead By Deadlight, the asynchronous multiplayer game from Behaviour Interactive is getting a new character: Nicholas Cage. The iconic actor is will be a playable survivor in an upcoming update on July 25th.

#IGN #SoG #Gaming
